  "title": "Bookstore Retail Cashier🌟| $2350",
  "description": "<p><strong> Bookstore Retail Cashier🌟| $2350 | Bedok, Bras Basah</strong></p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Cashiering: Operate the POS system to process purchases accurately 💳.</li><li>Customer Service: Assist with returns, exchanges, and ensuring customer satisfaction 😊.</li><li>Stock Management: Display merchandise, replenish stocks, assist in stock-taking, and receive orders 📦.</li><li>Store Operations: Maintain a clean, organized, and welcoming store environment 🧹.</li><li>Sales Optimization: Identify and capitalize on sales opportunities to enhance customer experience 📈.</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Work Schedule: 44 hours per week, 5-day work week (1 weekday off, 1 weekend off) 🗓️.</li><li>Retail Hours: Required for store operating hours.</li><li>A positive, customer-focused attitude and strong teamwork skills 💪.</li><li>Able to start at short notice 🏃‍♂️.</li></ul><p><strong>Why Join Us?</strong></p><p>Competitive starting salary 💸 and opportunities for career growth 🚀.<br />A dynamic, team-oriented work environment 🤝.<br />Full training provided to help you succeed in your role 🎓.<br /><br /><strong>📩 Apply Now</strong><br /><br />Submit your resume to<br /><br />📧 Email : annabelle.koh@crew.sg<br />📱 WhatsApp : 86852564<br /><br />Only shortlisted candidates will be notified.<br /><br />Annabelle Koh (R25158748)<br />Hrnet Ventures Pte Ltd - Crew by Hrnet<br />E.A.24C2435</p>",
